OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FTwo County Durham schools could be
OL,7,Fmerged as part of plans suggested by a
OL,8,Flocal authority.
OL,10,FProposals to combine Horndale County
OL,11,FInfant and Nursery School and St
OL,12,FFrancis Church of England (Aided)
OL,13,FJunior School in Newton Aycliffe into
OL,14,Fa Church of England Primary School
OL,15,Fhave been raised by Durham County
OL,16,FCouncil.
OL,18,FThe authority said the plans provide
OL,19,Fthe best future option for children,
OL,20,Fthe school, and the community.
