OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FHorndale School was rated 'Good' by
OL,7,FOfsted in October 2022 but in recent
OL,8,Fyears has been experiencing declining
OL,9,Fpupil numbers.
OL,11,FIn addition, the school has needed
OL,12,Fmore than #45,000 in financial support
OL,13,Fto address deficit issues.
OL,15,FDurham County Council also recently
OL,16,Flearned it is not sustainable to rely
OL,17,Fon future grants to balance the
OL,18,Fschool's budget.
