OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FSt Francis Church of England Junior
OL,7,FSchool has been chosen as a potential
OL,8,Fmerger partner due to its location
OL,9,Fnearby and feasibility.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the authority said:
OL,12,F"The school is in a good physical
OL,13,Fcondition with no immediate capital
OL,14,Fpriorities, it currently has surplus
OL,15,Fplaces allowing some of the classes
OL,16,Ffrom Horndale school to be
OL,17,Faccommodated on the main school site
OL,18,Fshould the proposal be agreed."
