OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FIt added: "We believe this proposal
OL,7,Fprovides the best future option for
OL,8,Fthe children, the school, and the
OL,9,Fcommunity it serves based on
OL,10,Feducational outcomes, pupil numbers,
OL,11,Fsite issues, and sustainable finances."
OL,13,FEducation officers at the council said
OL,14,Fthe breadth of the curriculum and the
OL,15,Fopportunity for social development of
OL,16,Fpupils within an all-through primary
OL,17,Fschool would be enhanced by pupils
OL,18,Fbeing educated on the St Francis site.
