OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FThis is furthered as St Francis is
OL,7,Fsaid to have extensive outdoor
OL,8,Flearning spaces.
OL,10,FShould the merger take place, the
OL,11,FHorndale County Infant and Nursery
OL,12,FSchool site could be repurposed for
OL,13,Fother uses.
OL,15,FRecent roof and window renovations
OL,16,Fmake the accommodation viable for
OL,17,Fother education purposes.
