OL,3,CTwo Durham schools could be merged
OL,4,Cunder local authority proposals
OL,6,FWithout merging the two schools, the
OL,7,Flocal authority warned it would "would
OL,8,Fpose a number of challenges around the
OL,9,Fappropriate allocation of education
OL,10,Fresources and an effective curriculum
OL,11,Fdelivery."
OL,13,FThe statement added: "Reputational
OL,14,Fdamage could affect the success of a
OL,15,Ffuture amalgamation and it must be
OL,16,Facknowledged that both governing
OL,17,Fbodies are aware of this."
OL,19,FParents have been asked to respond to
OL,20,Fthe plans by 20 October. A final
OL,21,Fdecision is due in January 2025.
